YOUR SESSION
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

{!Lead.RTS_Info_Session_Source__c}

You'll receive a separate Google Calendar invite shortly with the join link. If you don't see it within a few minutes, check your spam folder or email us at program-rts@ulem.org.

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
WHAT TO EXPECT
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

The info session runs about 45 minutes. We'll cover:

  •  What the RTS program is and who it's for
  •  The 10-week schedule and what your days look like
  •  Wraparound support (transportation, childcare, laptop, meals)
  •  Career outcomes and hiring partners
  •  Q&A — come with questions

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
THE PROGRAM, AT A GLANCE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

  •  10 weeks, Mon to Wed in-person (10 AM to 4 PM), Thu and Fri remote
  •  100% free. Wraparound support based on individual need.
  •  Cohort 1 starts May 11, 2026

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
READY TO APPLY?
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

You don't need to wait until after the info session. If you already know RTS is a fit, the application takes about 10 minutes:

Apply now: https://msimbo.org#apply

If you're not sure yet, come to the session first. No pressure.

Questions? Reply to this email.

